+.It Dv guid ,
+.It Dv leguid ,
+.It Dv beguid 
 A Globally Unique Identifier, parsed and printed as
 XXXXXXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXXXXXXXXXX.
 Its format is a string.
